decks.notes: This deck focuses on quickly ramping up mana using Mishra's Workshop and fast mana sources to play powerful artifacts like Karn, the Great Creator and The One Ring. It aims to overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures like Glaring Fleshraker and Patchwork Automaton while using cards like Manifold Key to control the board and generate card advantage. The goal is to establish a dominant board presence and quickly close out the game before the opponent has a chance to stabilize.
